    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">This Wearable 6&quot; Neck Knife is the perfect tool for anyone who needs convenient and quick access to their weapon in any situation With a fixed serrated blade, the knife is not only discrete and easy to carry at all times, it is effective in multiple ways. Thanks to its double sided blade with an extremely sharp tip, you can pierce most anything with this durable but compact design. The knife comes with a necklace style thick plastic sheath that offers protection and convenience with a lock in place pin to hold the knife handle down steadily.</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor 6.25&quot; Pocket Knife Stainless Steel Tactical Mini Clip Point Blade</h2>\n  <p>Compact yet durable, this 6.25 inch Mini Clip Point Fixed Blade Pocket Knife from ASR Outdoor is the perfect on the go companion for every day carry or outdoor excursions. Whether you&#039;re camping, hiking, hunting, or just need a dependable EDC gear knife, this mini fixed blade pocket knife delivers high performance in a compact form.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MINI FIXED BLADE KNIFE:</strong> Mini pocket knife features a three inch partial tang blade, a short quillon and plastic handle; ideal to include with general outdoor, hunting, camping or hiking gear where piercing, cutting tasks and smaller detail work are involved</li>\n    <li><strong>CLIP POINT BLADE:</strong> Features classic clip point design, where fixed blade leads to a thin and sharp tip; mini pocket knife fixed blade is made from reliable 440 stainless steel, designed to be rust and corrosion resistant with excellent edge retention</li>\n    <li><strong>KNIFE WITH SHEATH:</strong> For convenience, the mini fixed blade knife comes with faux leather sheath with snap closure, to keep blade secure and out of harms way when not in use</li>\n    <li><strong>LIGHTWEIGHT DESIGN:</strong> Mini pocket knife is very lightweight, weighing in at just 0.06lbs, making for easy handling and weightless carrying, adding virtually no weight or bulk to gear or if carried on person</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS:</strong> 6.5 x 1.5 x 0.25 inches; Weight: 0.06lb; Available in two colors</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1600x1600/undefinedASRO_KHK1117BH,KHK1118WH_main_parent.png\" alt=\"Compact yet durable, this 6.25 inch Mini Clip Point Fixed Blade Pocket Knife from ASR Outdoor is the perfect on the go companion for every day carry\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <p>Mini pocket knife features a three inch partial tang blade, a short quillon and plastic handle. The pocket knife boasts a classic clip point design, where fixed blade leads to a thin and sharp tip. And, crafted from 440 stainless steel, the blade boasts excellent sharpness and corrosion resistance. The clip point design offers precision control and versatility, making it ideal for tasks like slicing, cutting, and piercing, even through tough materials.</p>\n  <p>Available in two handle colors, blue or brown, the ergonomically designed handle provides a secure grip, enhancing comfort during use, while the small size ensures it fits easily into your pocket or gear without weighing you down. For convenience, the mini fixed blade knife comes with faux leather sheath with snap closure, to keep blade secure and out of harm’s way when not in use.</p>\n  <p>Weight: 0.06lbs Blade Length: 3.0 inches Full Length: 6.25 inches</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
